name: SNOWPEERCER | Pluto by Adesign
description:
SNOWPEERCER | Pluto by Adesign

Digital Illustration 
Dim.2000x2000 / Res.300x300
3.5 MB

Let me introduce you to the new generation of mech.snowpiercers thats haunting the snowlands of pluto. On the way to the home-station the cold storm getting more and more violant.
Harvesting the precious gems *XTZ* on this planet, this snow-trupper is loaded with it and have to arrive soon if he wants to come out there alive.

Enjoy the artwork and be part of an exciting journey with it.
Love ADS
